                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: AC-023 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "AC-001 Approved chart of accounts | Preventive | Reject posting to unapproved account | Critical | Controller. AC-002 Balanced journal required | Preventive | Reject unbalanced journal | Critical | Controller. AC-003 Journal approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved journal | Critical | Controller. AC-004 Period lock | Preventive | Reject posting to locked period | Critical | Controller. AC-005 Duplicate posting prevention | Preventive | Idempotent reject | Critical | Platform. AC-006 Subledger-to-GL reconciliation | Detective | Open reconciliation break | Critical | Accounting. AC-007 Bank-to-GL reconciliation | Detective | Open reconciliation break | Critical | Accounting. AC-008 Broker-to-GL reconciliation | Detective | Open reconciliation break | Critical | Accounting. AC-009 Intercompany balance matching | Detective | Flag mismatch | High | Accounting. AC-010 Elimination approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved elimination entry | Critical | Controller. AC-011 FX rate source | Preventive | Reject unapproved rate source | High | Controller. AC-012 Functional currency control | Preventive | Reject inconsistent currency use | Critical | Controller. AC-013 Fixed asset capitalization policy | Preventive | Reject non-conforming capitalization | High | Controller. AC-014 Depreciation approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved depreciation change | High | Controller. AC-015 AP vendor approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved vendor | Critical | Accounting. AC-016 AR customer approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved customer | High | Accounting. AC-017 Payment segregation | Preventive | Reject SoD conflict | Critical | Controller. AC-018 Close checklist completion | Preventive | Block close certification if incomplete | High | Controller. AC-019 Statement certification | Governance | Require CFO/Controller sign-off | Critical | CFO/Controller. AC-020 Restatement versioning | Evidence | Preserve prior version | Critical | Controller. AC-021 Material adjustment review | Preventive | Require independent review | Critical | CFO. AC-022 AI posting prohibition | Preventive | Deny AI posting permission | Critical | AI Governance. AC-023 Cross-tenant access denial | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. AC-024 Immutable audit trail | Evidence | Block mutation of posted record | Critical | Controller. AC-025 Backup and restore reconciliation | Detective | Verify post-restore integrity | Critical | Platform."
                            }
